data.description: This great home is not only close to Carnegie, but has all the comforts you'll need.  On a large , flat corner lot, you'll love the character of the angled front door.  As you enter,  you'll be impressed by its spacious rooms and open layout.  On the main level, hardwood flooring runs throughout the living room, kitchen, and dining room. The beautiful dark wood floors complement the new white Shaker-style kitchen cabinets and stainless steel appliances.  There is easy access to the back yard from the kitchen, with cute porches in the front and back of the home.  The back and front yard are completely fenced in.  No more living in tiny rooms, these bedrooms are large and spacious.  The master bedroom is large enough for a king sized bed with plenty of extra room.  Plenty of closet space as well in all rooms.  The bathroom has been completely updated.  All new doors and baseboard trim everywhere!  Roof, HVAC are all under 5 years old.  Easy access to Robinson and major thorofares.
